<div style="background-color:#2A313F;color:#FFFFFF;padding:40px;" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:4:6"><p style="text-align: center;">
	<span style="font-size:20px;">Christmas is the perfect time to tell the story of Jesus, spread the Good News, and share the joy He brings.</span>
</p>

<p style="text-align: center;">
	<span style="font-size:20px;">What better way to do this than our Advent devotional activity workbook!</span>
</p>

<p style="text-align: center;">
	<span style="font-size:20px;">It is designed for kids of all ages to learn about Jesus through Arts &amp; Crafts projects and all of the stories of Jesus throughout the Advent season.</span>
</p>

<p style="text-align: center;">
	<span style="font-size:20px;">Download the devotional activity book and share it with as many people as you can.</span>
</p>

<p style="text-align: center;">
	<span style="font-size:20px;">This is a wonderful way to get our kids excited about Jesus and the reasons we celebrate Him.</span>
</p>

